                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                <date>Octo 22 1850</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>Dear Doctor</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Mr. Newman</persName> one of the<lb/> most learned\n                Professors of the Hebrew<lb/> language we have had in the Country is<lb/> on a visit\n                to the <placeName>United States</placeName> to see<lb/> if there is any opening for\n                him either as<lb/> teacher or lecturer. He has instructed<lb/> some of the most\n                    <sic>preminet</sic><add>?</add> men in<lb/>\n                <placeName>England</placeName> and with his learning &amp; good character<lb/> would\n                have <sic>ammended</sic> any Chair<lb/> had he been willing to have\n                    <sic>surrenderd</sic> his<lb/> faith In this country it will be no obstacle<lb/>\n                to him and should there be any vacancy<lb/> in the <placeName>Maryland</placeName>\n                Colleges or as a lecturer<lb/> any where to which you can recommend<lb/> him I am\n                quite certain that you will<lb/> have no cause to regret it. He is a<lb/> plain\n                simple man in his habits &amp; manners<lb/> but one worthy of being cherished</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">always Dear Doctor</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">very truly yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">M M Noah</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>D. Joshua Cohen</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Baltimore</placeName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3f47h97p/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
